<\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Things to do in Villefranche-sur-Mer<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Villefranche-sur-Mer is the perfect day trip. The train from Nice to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Italy<\/a> stops here, and it&#x2019;s just a short ride (only a couple of minutes!). If you have the energy, you can even walk here in just under 2 hours.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112830\/Villefranche-sur-Mer7-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"villefranche sur mer french riviera\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"villefranche sur mer french riviera\" class=\"wp-image-63376 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112830\/Villefranche-sur-Mer7-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112830\/Villefranche-sur-Mer7-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112830\/Villefranche-sur-Mer7-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112830\/Villefranche-sur-Mer7-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112830\/Villefranche-sur-Mer7-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112830\/Villefranche-sur-Mer7-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112830\/Villefranche-sur-Mer7-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112830\/Villefranche-sur-Mer7-683x10