ave<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-wander-the-old-town-streets\">Wander the Old Town Streets<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The old town is the heart of Villefranche-sur-Mer and the most wonderful part of the town. Most buildings are from the 12th or 13th century and have been beautifully preserved. What&#x2019;s more, all the houses are painted in rainbow colors with shutters, plants, and flowers to match. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/villefranche-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book a hotel in Villefranche-sur-Mer<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112751\/Villefranche-sur-Mer3-556x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"232\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-63367 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 556px) 100vw, 556px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112751\/Villefranche-sur-Mer3-556x810.jpg 556w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112751\/Villefranche-sur-Mer3-412x600.jpg 412w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112751\/Villefranche-sur-Mer3-232x338.jpg 232w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.c