r the old town. Spooky!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11.jpg\" alt=\"villefranche-sur-mer pastel houses french riviera\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"villefranche-sur-mer pastel houses french riviera\" class=\"wp-image-63384 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31112908\/Villefranche-sur-Mer11-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sta