nne\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The historical village of Aubeterre-sur-Dronne<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/62992&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31151011\/villefranche-sur-mer-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31151011\/villefranche-sur-mer-1-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/31151011\/villefranche-sur-mer-1-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Villefranche-sur-Mer: Visit the Most Colorful Town in South France\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-st-pierre-chapel\">St Pierre Chapel<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>St Pierre Chapel is the biggest surprise of all in Villefranche-sur-Mer! The 16th-century chapel was once used as a storage area by the local fishermen during the 19th century. Later, Jean Cocteau (a famous artist and film director) found a special place in his heart for the church. Because of this, when it was renovated in the 1950s, he painted murals of the local fisherman, depicting their lives in Villefranche. It&#x2019;s a beautiful place to spend some time on your trip.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Opening times<\/strong>: Open Wednesday-Sunday (closed on Tuesdays and at lunchtime)<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Entry fee:<\/strong> 3 Euros for adults<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30133637\/nice-france-11.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera villefranche-sur-mer \"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera villefranche-sur-mer \" class=\"wp-image-63308 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30133637\/nice-france-11.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30133637\/nice-france-11-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30133637\/nice-france-11-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30133637\/nice-france-11-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30133637\/nice-france-11-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/30133637\/ni